options.text: May I have a resource flyer?

d066c87d-8a34-4ea6-a06e-642dd2ccadd9.title: Shield master
d066c87d-8a34-4ea6-a06e-642dd2ccadd9.text:
Although archers like myself like to keep distance from
our enemies, it's always good to have a bit of protection.

8d459d06-5b92-4535-bb83-9761bfe5e380.title: <player>
8d459d06-5b92-4535-bb83-9761bfe5e380.text: Very sensible! Did you make these youself?

fc7ff109-1dde-42ad-8e48-ab31c114cd52.title: Shield master
fc7ff109-1dde-42ad-8e48-ab31c114cd52.text:
I am a bit of a craftsman, I indeed made all these
shields.

93607910-4158-4059-ba39-6e15d5d16202.title: Shield master
93607910-4158-4059-ba39-6e15d5d16202.text:
It's very simple! First you'll need to be skilled in
crafting and fletching, the exact details you can find in
your skill guide.

ffe05fff-9198-4145-a56a-78c18ff5b6f3.title: Shield master
ffe05fff-9198-4145-a56a-78c18ff5b6f3.text:
For every shield, you'll require some tools! A knife for
fletching the wood and a hammer for crafting the shield.

dfaba3c1-cd1a-4bbd-819f-d440f14658d7.title: Shield master
dfaba3c1-cd1a-4bbd-819f-d440f14658d7.text:
As for resources, you'll need 2 logs, 2 pieces of tanned
leather and 15 nails.

ab4b6439-6dcc-4864-9245-110bd45478c2.title: <player>
ab4b6439-6dcc-4864-9245-110bd45478c2.text:
Where can I find out more information about the
resources needed?

bc82c1e0-0df1-4ced-8563-46c93db0455b.title: Shield master
bc82c1e0-0df1-4ced-8563-46c93db0455b.text:
I have a flyer! It details all the shields and the
resources needed for them.

4f436174-c526-4667-9e8c-a54b429cc7f2.title: <player>
4f436174-c526-4667-9e8c-a54b429cc7f2.text: May I have a resource flyer?

63c55e15-bf55-4814-bb4a-a314f99f41e4.title: Shield master
63c55e15-bf55-4814-bb4a-a314f99f41e4.text: Of course! The more you know, the better!

720313c6-7933-4325-b1b1-a9f5542bda1e.text:
The Shield Master hands you 'Leather Shields -
Resource information flyer'.

46fcadbf-ed42-4bf4-a718-c190603e75d2.title: Shield master
46fcadbf-ed42-4bf4-a718-c190603e75d2.text:
My name is William! And I'll tell you this, I'm the best
crossbowman this side of White Wolf Mountain.

c95f83c4-84b1-430d-96ee-d04a03b7f9f9.title: <player>
c95f83c4-84b1-430d-96ee-d04a03b7f9f9.text:
Who's better than you on the other side of the
mountain?

765f3bbc-15e0-44e3-87cb-27484c87df1b.title: Shield master
765f3bbc-15e0-44e3-87cb-27484c87df1b.text: Couldn't tell you that myself, never been there.

81a79dfd-22fa-4afc-b1a8-20a75b1c8358.title: <player>
81a79dfd-22fa-4afc-b1a8-20a75b1c8358.text: Oh... How did you come across that crossbow then?

1b9f42f0-2524-43e1-a2f0-7655217e099b.title: Shield master
1b9f42f0-2524-43e1-a2f0-7655217e099b.text:
Oh this? Some wandering merchant came by recently,
told me it was the stealthiest crossbow there was.

6c5cec0c-fdf6-4f47-b2ea-2bf1888464f0.title: Shield master
6c5cec0c-fdf6-4f47-b2ea-2bf1888464f0.text:
Well, he told me it was his last one too, so I figured I'd
give it a try.

71e534de-b0dd-4fe8-bbb1-3fa7dd2e194a.title: <player>
71e534de-b0dd-4fe8-bbb1-3fa7dd2e194a.text: It was nice meeting you William.

74e09786-b514-4910-8a71-34a25a76d781.title: Shield master
74e09786-b514-4910-8a71-34a25a76d781.text: You already have a flyer. I've only so many left.

918df5e8-9e7b-4a36-b970-01be3ca02d6d.title: Shield master
918df5e8-9e7b-4a36-b970-01be3ca02d6d.text: Stay protected adventurer, for it's dangerous out there.
